// Filename: bitstream_unittest.cs
//
// Description: Unit tests for the VP8 keyframe header writer (encoder side,
// src/bitstream.cs). Cross-checks bit-exactly against libvpx's keyframe
// header path, and verifies the produced bytes parse back through the
// existing decoder's frame-tag parser to recover the correct dimensions
// and frame type.
//
// The expected reference bytes were generated by compiling a standalone
// build of the libvpx vp8/encoder/bitstream.c keyframe path and feeding
// it the same configurations used here. Any divergence indicates a bug
// in the C# port.
//
// Author(s):
// Claude Opus 4.7 (Anthropic AI assistant, model: claude-opus-4-7), commissioned by Aaron Clauson
